videos.description: Florida's Jalen Hudson drives to the rim and finishes with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Florida's Hudson throws down thunderous one-handed slam

videos.description: Florida's Gorjok Gak collects the missed shot and finishes it off with a dunk.
videos.headline: Florida's Gak gets putback jam off board

videos.description: Clemson's Marcquise Reed makes Florida's Egor Koulechov look silly and finishes the shot with the contact.
videos.headline: Clemson's Reed puts moves on defender and finishes

videos.description: Clemson's Marcquise Reed connects with Elijah Thomas on a full-court pass for a dunk putting Clemson up 69-68 with just over 30 seconds left.
videos.headline: Clemson collects air ball, hits full court pass for go-ahead dunk

videos.description: Clemson's late dunk with just over 30 seconds left helps lift the Tigers over Florida 69-68.
videos.headline: Clemson fights back to upset No. 22 Florida
